### Login admin
POST http://localhost:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@local",
  "password": "adminpass"
}

### List posts (public)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts

### Create post (auth)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Post desde API",
  "contenido": "Contenido de prueba",
  "categoria_id": 1
}

### Get comments of post 1
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/1/comments

### Create comment (auth)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "texto": "Buen post"
}

### Delete comment (auth)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>
